  "detailed_description": "<br><br>\"Light and Shadow - Doppelganger\" is an RPG game produced by Geocentrism Theory and published by Hanabi games.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Plot</h2>In this cruel world, Nora's originally happy life is over in a flash. In order to repay the kindness of her adoptive parents, she resolutely embarks on the path of revenge. <br>Will she become a revered paladin or an assassin of darkness?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248120/extras/108376c15319e9cce42e477764d3f2df.avif?t=1743233653\" width=551 height=369 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Content</h2>This game is a role-playing type of game.  Player controls the main character, Rora. Go through a series of thrilling adventures. Will she be able to break through the many obstacles to achieve her goal?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248120/extras/4858510ba94b92e7d2cf88e8e0fc91d8.avif?t=1743233653\" width=550 height=310 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248120/extras/3e1487de36add5e406f17f756e7467c4.avif?t=1743233653\" width=550 height=311 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248120/extras/301d698ab8243f8c24948cdb3133f589.avif?t=1743233653\" width=550 height=311 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Jrpg<br></li><li>Rich storyline<br></li><li>Voice acting</li></ul>",
